column5: Did some top water action on Seymour and made a video.The Duo Pencil 110 is becoming one of my favourite top water lures.I got them locally from this shophttps://www.facebook.com/BassCityFishingWatch in HD[media=x,500,375,0]
Great contribution guy. Thanks. Nothing like sight fishing top waters.
You girly men and your boca grips!!!        Great vid man!
Great video! Thanks.  Last time i fished Seymour caught a wicked 40 inch musky. That was 15 yrs. ago. Wonder if the musky are still there or if the pike pushed them away.
